data.title: Jessica Chastain Snaps Selfies in N.Y.C., Plus Justin Chon and Awkwafina, Lin-Manuel Miranda and More
data.meta_description: Jessica Chastain hits The Eyes of Tammy Faye premiere in N.Y.C., Justin Chon and Awkwafina pose at the Blue Bayou premiere in L.A., and Lin-Manuel Miranda celebrates the return of Broadway. See what your favorite stars are up to!
data.text:
